{"word":"G2310 - θεμέλιος - themélios - them-el'-ee-os - Foundation","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεμέλιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">themélios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">them-el'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Foundation</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆதாரம், அஸ்திபாரம் - பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the foundation (of a building, wall, city)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; something <i>put</i> down, that is, a <i>substruction</i> (of a building, etc.), (literally or figuratively): - foundation.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2310/2310\">G2310</a>, <a href=\"#/G2311/2311\">G2311</a>"}]}